name: Interprof Communica & Collab
fullname: Foundations of Interprofessional Communication and Collaboration
info: Interprofessional approach to health care. Directed group activities in five two-hour sessions: personal/professional image; teamwork, self/peer assessment; health professions; professional identity/integrity; relationships between professions and those they serve. Includes online modules.prereq: Enrolled CLSP or OT student
